channel.title: My Skiller, Pics and Goals
channel.description:
Hey,
My main lost membership and I was browsing through Fagex runescape guides, and saw the sticky to make a level 3 skiller. I figured, what the fuck, why not. Since I couldn't use my main until I got back membership, I started a new account. My first goal is 99 Fishing/Cooking. After that I'll sell all my cooked. I have enough feathers to get to at least 89 fishing, then I'll switch to lobsters in the fishing guild. Here's pics of my character now. I don't do anything illegal so don't bother reporting me. The 2.8M I made by merchanting feathers to get enough cash to get 100k feathers, and I decided to stay on it. I'm flyfishing until I run out of feathers, which will be in about 3590 trips. I've been training for a total of a week and a half. I am really into this, and I love getting reported 5 times an hour. =)
Bank: [img]http://img525.imageshack.us/img525/6241/uploadud8.png[/img]
Skills: [img]http://img165.imageshack.us/img165/8126/uploadep0.png[/img]
If I cooked all my raws I'd have 65-66 cooking, so don't call me a noob.
